  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether women with postpartum major depressive
      disorder (MDD) will experience a significant decrease in depressive symptoms from baseline
      over an eight-week treatment intervention with escitalopram (Lexapro). Also, to determine
      whether women with postpartum MDD will experience a significant decrease in anxiety symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
